The launcher used to activate demo APP in dual-display wayland desktop of Yocto.

It requires to plug a keyboard and a mouse.
Mouse is used to generate a mouse input device to feed simulated mouse movement.
Keyboard is used to choose left/right monitor and demo APP.  

How to use the script:

keyboard: "left" and "right" key: move mouse cursor to choose to activate APP on left or right monitor
keyboard: number key "0"~"9": choose different DEMO APP